{"tid":237041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再被申請破產　梅媽庭上鬧呈請人夠晒毒","createTime":"2017-05-10T06:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T07:58:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff85d71f529385b6f40c422ec773fd50c4fa76d","tid":237041,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170510/photo/bkn-20170510134354739-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170510140335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170510134354739-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170510140335&h=e83d3970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年05月10日(三) 13:43<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">梅媽今年3月再被債權人入稟高院申請將她破產。(溫卓賢攝)</span><br />\n已故樂壇天后梅艷芳的93歲母親覃美金(梅媽)，過去因屢次興訟要求一次過取得梅艷芳遺產，最終因敗訴而欠下巨額訟費，並於2012年被頒令破產，直至去年4月破產期始完結，但她今年3月再被債權人入稟高院申請將她破產。案件今在破產聆案官席前提訊，梅媽親自到庭。據庭上披露，是次破產呈請是由梅媽的前破產受託人提出，因梅媽早前與其有訴訟，並於2014年被法庭頒令需支付對方訟費，但她一直無支付，直至今年1月，她共欠訟費連利息共13.4萬多港元，故才被其作破產呈請。<br />\n<br />\n梅媽今表示願意償還款項，並已寫好支票，但指自己的銀行戶口被對方凍結，故未能使用戶口內的20多萬港元。梅媽庭上直斥對方指：「佢都夠晒毒啦，吸血咁吸晒我&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n不過聆案官指，梅媽未能拿出證據證明自己的戶口確有20多萬港元且正被凍結，亦未能證明是呈請人凍結其戶口，故最後決定把案件押後至5月17日再訊，並要梅媽再向銀行查詢，並要她要求銀行發出信件證實其說法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170510/bkn-20170510134354739-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170510%2Fbkn-20170510134354739-0510_00822_001.html&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=75ee18a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170510/bkn-20170510134354739-0510_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b9e8977fbc269afc1a59cf8b7018ab5c01cbdde8","tid":237041,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c4d77bc31cdc9bd2eb8cdb90c91655b6c1e9e9","tid":237041,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"好撚煩"},{"pid":"35d73f86fe988644da45ea9bd7547b4c9b91bbd8","tid":237041,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"呢條廢老幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8f887ed464b8c4895f8e1984b651088e669394","tid":237041,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:27:44.000Z","msg":"梅姐副身家仲有幾多？"},{"pid":"0dcef1a0fb89587ecac188e49ee337edef226290","tid":237041,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"俾佢攞曬益個仆街仔 唔俾佢最後益左啲垃圾慈善機構可能攞黎幫啲支那蝗 不如派俾港柒啦"},{"pid":"7bd76fa9b80633e360432ee32264f2ae4d4917fe","tid":237041,"uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢條廢老幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估佢至少一百歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332bfe69595a0e9f62d9bb8ac06fbec4497b80d5","tid":237041,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢條廢老幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估佢至少一百歲命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百二啦"},{"pid":"c2ff8cdfd7e69515c97cacd3b1dd82176931c532","tid":237041,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8252058748ba53801987c549673b562b319f9116","tid":237041,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行過路過入黎睇下啦喂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼指大後又一垃圾學